  "prompt": "Which is the best C programming training institute in Bhubaneswar?",
  "response": "I don't have real-time data or specific rankings for training institutes. However, to find the best C programming training institute in Bhubaneswar, you can consider the following steps:\n\n1. **Research Online**: Look for reviews and ratings on platforms like Google, Facebook, or educational forums. Websites like Justdial, UrbanPro, or Sulekha can also provide information on local institutes.\n\n2. **Check Course Curriculum**: Make sure the institute covers all fundamental and advanced topics in C programming and offers practical sessions.\n\n3. **Instructors' Qualifications**: Research the qualifications and experience of the instructors. Experienced trainers can provide better insights and guidance.\n\n4. **Alumni Feedback**: Reach out to former students to get their opinions on the training quality and placement assistance.\n\n5. **Visit the Institute**: If possible, visit the institute to get a feel for the environment, facilities, and classroom setup.\n\n6. **Compare Fees**: Look at the fee structure and see if it aligns with your budget while also considering the value of the training provided.\n\n7. **Placement Assistance**: Check if the institute offers any placement assistance or industry connections.\n\nSome known institutes in Bhubaneswar that you can start with include:\n- NIIT\n- Aptech\n- C-DAC\n- Techno India\n\nAlways cross-reference and verify any information you gather to ensure you make an informed decision.",
